{"_id":"1cc80d22-02c8-43a4-91fa-98ad97e6ffc9","type":"ability","name":"Know Your Enemy","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Know Your Enemy","rank":"5","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"intuition","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"You learn the target's vulnerabilities, resistances, immunities, stats, and trained skills. If the target successfully defends, you may not attempt to cast this spell against them again for 24 hours.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"26562833-0462-4952-b8c1-e87ddd915ffe","type":"ability","name":"Rune of Finding","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Rune of Finding","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"This rune can be used to locate individuals, members of a particular species, substances, or objects within great distances.\nWhen used on its own, you must engrave this on an object that can be held or worn, and you must engrave it to find a specific substance, species, object, or individual with whom you are familiar. When activated you know the distance and direction to the nearest match to your parameters within 500 meters. This lasts for as long as you maintain the effect.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"38c40584-66c3-415b-80ea-514b68b69254","type":"ability","name":"Telepathy Rune","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Telepathy Rune","rank":"3","type":"rune","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"This rune can be used to communicate telepathically.\nWhen used on its own, this rune must be engraved in pairs (a pair only counts as a single rune). When activated, creatures carrying or wearing the objects on which they are engraved are able to share senses and knowledge at will, allowing them to communicate with each other. You may also choose one skill when engraving the rune: the affected creatures share that skill and may use the higher of their two ranks.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"417c2d3e-be8b-4f8d-ad5c-f110dea4b48e","type":"ability","name":"Location Rune","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Location Rune","rank":"1","type":"rune","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"Maintained","cost":"1","description":"This rune can be used to direct senses to a given location.\nWhen used on its own, once activated you know the exact distance and location to the rune for as long as you maintain the effect.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"46cf92b2-71d2-4a6e-b76a-16479e11d877","type":"ability","name":"Remote Viewing Rune","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Remote Viewing Rune","rank":"3","type":"rune","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"This rune can be used to project senses to it.\nWhen used on its own, when activated, you can see and hear as though you were at the location of the rune for as long as you maintain the effect.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"4c273d39-7f19-4f3e-a096-51188ca9a74a","type":"skill","name":"Clairvoyance","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill_id":"clairvoyance","domain":"Arcana","rank":1,"stat":"intelligence","description":"Rather than obscuring or obfuscating, as is done in illusion magic, clairvoyance is used to alter the mind in beneficial ways, extending one's senses to see what others cannot, or even that which has not yet occurred."}}
{"_id":"5368dae8-11b9-4a54-a2c0-10c455f948de","type":"ability","name":"Memory Delving Rune","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Memory Delving Rune","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"This rune can be used to extract and read memories.\nWhen used on its own, it can be used to delve into the memories of a creature in the area of the rune when activated. When you first affect the target, you must make a Clairvoyance check to gain access to their surface thoughts and short-term memory (about 5 minutes). On a success, you may make another check to gain access to their long term memory. On a success, you may make another check to gain access to repressed or hidden memories. The target cannot willingly fail to defend against the last check. If you fail any check, the effect ends immediately and you may not affect the target for another 24 hours.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"620a435d-b72a-4d79-a658-b25a15feb1a3","type":"ability","name":"Detection Rune","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Detection Rune","rank":"1","type":"rune","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"This rune can be used to sense events and magic.\nWhen used on its own, this allows you to detect magic within a Short range of the rune, and you may also identify its purpose if you succeed at a Clairvoyance check.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"9293c201-07c7-49ba-b614-d56ec032c05b","type":"ability","name":"Clairvoyant Targeting","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Clairvoyant Targeting","rank":"1","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"","target":"Self","range":"","duration":"Next","cost":"1","description":"Until the end of your next turn, you may use your Clairvoyance skill ranks to make attacks with a weapon of your choice.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
{"_id":"a090440b-a994-4e6d-8dfc-95a33feff9a3","type":"ability","name":"Mindreading","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/clairvoyance.svg","system":{"skill":"Clairvoyance","name":"Mindreading","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"intelligence","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"You can read your target's surface thoughts (anything they are currently thinking about) without them knowing. You gain a Boon to all social interactions with them. You also gain a Boon to defend against any of their attacks as well as to all attacks you make against them. If the target successfully defends against this, they become aware of the intrusion and you may not affect them again for 24 hours.","domain":"Arcana","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"clairvoyance"}}
